16:["$","p",null,{"children":"Etsy SEO isn't about gaming an algorithm — it's about communicating clearly to both Etsy's search engine and the humans searching on it. Your title, tags, and description work together as a system. When all three reinforce the same buyer-intent keywords, Etsy's algorithm has everything it needs to rank you for the searches that matter."}]
17:["$","p",null,{"children":"The challenge is that this takes real research — studying competitor listings, using keyword tools, and rewriting copy that reads naturally while hitting all the right signals. Most sellers don't have time to do this well for every listing."}]
